      • addItem

        public boolean addItem(int bookId,
                       int quantity)
        Adds a new book id into the map of current books
        Parameters:
        bookId - the id of the book to add
        quantity - the quantity of book to add
        Returns:
        boolean true if there is enough stock available to add the item into the cart or else false (false too when the book does not exist)

      • removeItem

        public boolean removeItem(int bookId,
                          int quantity)
        Removes the specified of the book from the cart session. If the quantity is greater than the quantity contained in the cart, it will simply remove the entry.
        Parameters:
        bookId - the id of the book to remove
        quantity - the quantity of books to remove
        Returns:
        true if the removal operation is sucessful or false if the cart does not contain the specified book

      • getCart

        public Map<Book,Integer> getCart()
        Gets the cart map composed of the books entity (key) linked to the quantity in the cart (value).
        Returns:
        the cart map

      • confirmOrder

        public Order confirmOrder(String email)
        Creates the order for the current user based on the current cart
        Parameters:
        email - the email address of the owner
        Returns:
        the order made by the user or null if the cart was empty at first or if there is not enough quantity available in stock
